'''Marianna Zorba''' is a   and a music teacher. She loves ethnic and . In 1997 she represented Greece in the 42nd . She was engaged to the composer of her song, , during the week before the grand finale in . A few weeks after the contest they got married. Marianna and the song () scored 39 points and reached 12th place. The Greek press turned against Marianna and that led her to her decision to stop singing professionally.
